data.description:
**3% for buyers agent.  
**PART of the loan is assumable at 2.99% interest.
Beautiful 4 bed/2 bath home in Tansi! Watch the cows come up to the fence from your back porch. Nestled between woods on both sides and no one directly across the street, you feel secluded yet in a beautiful neighborhood! The family room is at the center of the home with a gas fireplace.  Beautiful scenery from the dining room over looking the farm. Approx. 1000 sq ft has been added to this home in the last couple of years. Including a 4th bedroom with large walk in closet (could be a mother in law suite), a walk in pantry that leads to a hidden crawl space, and nice second entry way. Also, a heated & cooled office in the detached garage. The master has its own bathroom with double vanity as well as a walk in closet! 
This home is just a couple minutes from all of Tansi amenities. Including golf, swimming, lake, and more. You have to see this home to see it’s beauty! For more information, call Anthony at (765) 621-0937. Appointment only
